Description: Slope Determination by Analysis of Residuals (SDAR) for automated 
    and objective linear-fitting of mechanical test-data 
    (see: standard ASTM E3076-18 â‰¤doi:10.1520/E3076-18> or a detailed 
    description in E. Lucon (2019) <doi:10.6028/NIST.TN.2050>). As the 
    SDAR-algorithm heavily uses linear regressions, a faster version is 
    additionally available to find the optimum region for the (one) final 
    linear regression by random sub-sampling within the normalized range of the 
    test-data.
